description:
The Real Housewives of New Jersey is BACK and the premiere was A+! Danny welcomes Margaret Josephs and Dolores Catania to talk about the premiere, what's to come, and more! After the interview, Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Dallas, which featured a cast trip, a chicken named Patsy Cline, and more!


Dolores/Margaret Interview: 4:06ish

RHOD Recap: 30:42ish
